18.description:
How MiName Works?

Search for Product In the past, direct marketing by phone, text or email has proven to be an annoyance for internet users, whose personal information is so casually shared amongst companies seeking a larger client base. In addition to being invasive to consumers, the companies trying to market themselves are spending good money on a form of marketing with a notoriously low conversion rate because of its lack of a specific, interested target market.

MiName.co.za is an innovative recommendations site that turns a lose-lose situation into a mutually beneficial partnership between our partners and the consumers who are actively seeking their services. Whatever your industry, there’s no need to continue wasting resources with call centres which offer a notoriously low conversion rate.

The advantages for consumers extend beyond increased privacy and internet searching convenience, too. MiName offers customers great money-back deals for signing up, making purchases, sharing their experience via social media and reviewing products. By choosing the companies that they would like to contact them, consumers have unprecedented online privacy of their personal details.
